c: 10
v: 15
t: "When Our clear revelations are recited to them, those who entertain no hope of meeting Us say to you: \"Bring us a Qur’an different than this or make some changes in it.\" O Muhammad, tell them: \"It is not possible for me to change it myself. I follow only what is revealed to me. Indeed, I cannot disobey my Lord, for I fear the punishment of a Mighty Day"